# Image Folder

Place your high-quality images here with the following names:

## Required Images:

### Home Page:
- hero-background.jpg (1920x1080px recommended)
- mercedes-e-class.jpg (800x600px)
- mercedes-s-class.jpg (800x600px)
- mercedes-v-class.jpg (800x600px)

### About Page:
- about-luxury-car.jpg (800x600px)
- professional-chauffeur.jpg (800x600px)
- chauffeur-service.jpg (800x600px)

### Services Page:
- airport-transfer.jpg (800x600px)
- corporate-travel.jpg (800x600px)
- special-events.jpg (800x600px)
- long-distance.jpg (800x600px)

### Fleet Page:
- mercedes-e-class-main.jpg (1200x800px)
- mercedes-s-class-main.jpg (1200x800px)
- mercedes-v-class-main.jpg (1200x800px)

## Image Guidelines:

- Use high-quality, professional photos
- Optimize images for web (compress without losing quality)
- Recommended format: JPG for photos, PNG for logos
- Consider using WebP format for better performance
- All images should have descriptive alt text (already included in HTML)
- Ensure images are properly licensed for commercial use

## Image Optimization Tools:

- TinyPNG (https://tinypng.com/)
- Squoosh (https://squoosh.app/)
- ImageOptim (Mac)
- GIMP (Free, cross-platform)

## Stock Photo Resources:

- Unsplash (https://unsplash.com/)
- Pexels (https://pexels.com/)
- Pixabay (https://pixabay.com/)

Note: Make sure you have the rights to use any images on your website.
